name: Experiment Or Die #84
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. 4th installment of #TheCoolAlphabet with the letter J. Not only is the film itself a masterpiece but the illustration and branding for the film was exceptional as well. I also visited Universal Studios in Florida when I was a kid and got to see the Jaws interactive shark show...it was rad. I've always been fond of sharks. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
